{"type":"answer","id":104880,"parentType":"question","parentId":13288,"uid":15246,"contents":"反共就更要學習共產黨的思想了；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/KHVJ6dB.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KHVJ6dB.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/KHVJ6dB.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n我現在每天堅持看新聞聯播，解讀言下之意；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/QYG9jp5.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QYG9jp5.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/QYG9jp5.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n相信明居正老師等研究共產黨的學者，必定是每天拿著人民日報字字必究；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NVmcfxg.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NVmcfxg.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NVmcfxg.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n建議換一個角度去看待考政治，學習共匪理論並不代表你認同呢，以反共的角度說不定更有意思；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qOcTEkd.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qOcTEkd.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qOcTEkd.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n就是考解答題的時候不要直接反共就行；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1AXInz3.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1AXInz3.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1AXInz3.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n知識改變命運，樓主加油！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/yavCZfF.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yavCZfF.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/yavCZfF.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-14","agreeCount":8,"discussionCount":2}